728788f-b.text:
752 Delafield Ave., adjoining the S.W. corner of Clove Road. This house was owned by one named Smith according to Beers' map of 1874. Later, it was the property of A.A. Mitchell (1898-1907 maps).
This is a set of two views taken the same day.
July 2, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
